long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension Features:

1. Cycle through Squid Game 2 wallpapers each time a new tab is opened.
2. Choose a random Squid Game 2 background or set a favorite in the wallpaper selection panel.
3. Search bar where result from user preferred search engine.
4. Direct links to your email and social media profiles.
5. Automatically displays the current date and time.
6. New Note feature to jot down your tasks.
7. Quick links to frequently visited websites.
8. Convenient access to your bookmarks.
9. Shortcut panel to add and access favorite websites quickly.
10. Immediate access to Google applications.
11. Explore more themes easily.
12. Share content directly to social media.
13. Download wallpapers with one click.
14. One-click access to online games.
15. Activate entertaining animations like snow, rain, falling leaves, or fireworks on your Squid Game 2 themed new tab.
